# AhaDiff

Use AhaDiff after meaningful code changes to turn the current diff into
verified learn-back artifacts.

Preferred commands:

- `ahadiff learn HEAD~1..HEAD`
- `ahadiff learn --staged`
- `ahadiff quiz <run_id>`
- `ahadiff review`
- `ahadiff verify <run_id>`

Prefer generated explanations with verified claims and file-line evidence.
Keep provider secrets in environment variables and do not commit private
`.ahadiff/` audit logs.
